 "name": "RPlog_Psychology_101",
 "title": "Psychology 101",
 "summary": "Aboard a docked freighter, Paul Nighman stands guard duty with the young Shenner asleep at his feet when the cheerful Amylynn enters. Over the course of a quiet stretch, the small band of travelers -- Paul, Shenner, Amylynn, and dignitaries including Leia Organa Solo and Winter -- pass the time in conversation that drifts toward matters of the heart and mind. The relaxed, character-driven scene digs into the psychology and tangled feelings of the group as they rest between dangers.",
